room_title: Escape room "Art Gallery Heist" by Gateway Escape Rooms in St. Louis
room_address: 150 Concord Plaza Shopping Center Sappington, MO 63128
room_description: Improvements found in this Art Gallery escape room include the use of original works of art purpose-built for the room. Visual, audio and tactile clues abound. The room is full of artifacts and fixtures that look like sculpture but yield clues. In this room players can expect to find a few fun surprises, too.
